    "We use the term Responsible Gambling (RG) throughout this paper as it is commonly used to describe these practices.",
    "We acknowledge the ongoing and important discourse contrasting the RG framework to safer gambling or public health approaches, but a full discussion of that debate is beyond the scope of this paper.",
    "For examples of standardized reporting guidelines and checklists for ML models and AI-based systems, see TRIPOD-AI (Collins et al., 2024), CONSORT-AI (Liu et al., 2020),SPIRIT-AI (Cruz Rivera et al., 2020).",
    "For example, the UK Gambling Commission fined Corbett Bookmakers £0.7m in March 2025, where one identified issue was \"failing to identify a consumer who staked £23,674 in a 13-day period as someone who may be at risk of or experiencing harms associated with gambling\" (https://www.gamblingcommission.gov.uk/news/article/gbp686-070-fine-for-corbett-bookmakers-limited).",
    "See, for example, public aggregations of these benchmarks at epoch.ai/benchmarks and artificialanalysis.ai."
